---
title: Chipotle Black Bean Tacos with Charred Capsicum Salsa & Cheddar
description: There's a whole lot of goodness packed into these handheld delights – and we're not just talking about the fibre-rich black beans and vitamin-packed veggies. With our mild chipotle sauce, Tex-Mex spice blend and soft and supple mini flour tortillas, it's the perfect mix of nutrition and deliciousness. Dig in!
